"content": "<h2>Grinding using a hand mill</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod11:5\">EXO 11:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:41\">MAT 24:41</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:35\">LUK 17:35</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:8\">NUM 11:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:21\">JDG 16:21</a> <em>Samson doing a woman's work</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa47:2\">ISA 47:2</a></p>\n<h2>Grinding grain into flour</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:20\">NUM 15:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num15:21\">NUM 15:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:10\">2CH 2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:37\">NEH 10:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:10\">JOB 31:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa28:28\">ISA 28:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:30\">EZK 44:30</a></p>\n<h2>Grinding incense</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod30:36\">EXO 30:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:12\">LEV 16:12</a></p>\n<h2>Grinding as an act of destruction</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:21\">DEU 9:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:15\">2KI 23:15</a></p>\n<h2>Grinding used figuratively</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa3:15\">ISA 3:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:22\">PRO 27:22</a></p>",
